<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> Bygner, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> zu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, und
                                <expan>Concze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Treppendorff<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger,</ex></expan> und <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> als von eins totslags
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr gnade <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz des
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>C<ex>oncze</ex></expan>
<expan>Treppendorff<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> niht ist, daz wir
                            <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> niht mechtig sein. Denn wir
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>oncze</ex></expan>
<expan>Treppendorff<ex>er</ex></expan> durch <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> für uns besant und
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu rede gesaczt; der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, wie wol in der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>eincz</ex></expan> Bygner iren <expan>vatt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erslag<ex>en</ex></expan> hab, so <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        dennoch er und sein <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> nehst zu
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gleich<ex>er</ex></expan> teyding, als sie bedunkt,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>folgt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> also, daz sie zwen ausz dem rate zu
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz der ewr, <expan>H<ex>eincz</ex></expan>
                        Bygner, <expan>desgleich<ex>en</ex></expan> auch zwen ausz dem rate zu
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hett. Und <expan>möcht<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        die vier ein <expan>richtigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>getroff<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, so <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> die sach
                        bericht <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>möcht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> die vier niht
                                <expan>üb<ex>er</ex>einkome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, daz denn
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>er</ex></expan> und sein
                            <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>fünft<ex>en</ex></expan> ausz
                        dem rate zu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> darczu
                            <expan>sölt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> fünf oder
                        ir der <expan>mer<ex>er</ex>teyl</expan> denn der sache zu
                                <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> rich<expan>tigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>sölt<ex>en</ex></expan> gewaltig <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        sein. <expan>Sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> teyding sey in der
                                <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>eincz</ex></expan> Bygner, der ewr,
                            <expan>ausgang<ex>en</ex></expan> und wölt des niht
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>folgen,</expan> als sie das mit dem rate zu
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> wol
                            <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> machen <expan>müg<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        daz er <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> on <expan>sein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> darczu niht <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> sich teyding <expan>v<ex>er</ex>fahen</expan>
                        könne. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
